thread.title: Michelle
thread.title_full: TAXIBOX mobile self-storage reviewed by Michelle

author: Michelle
title: Michelle
text: When in between houses we stored our things in 3 taxi boxes. Everything went smoothly, from the drop off of our boxes, the pick up and the storage of them, to the redelivey to our new house 4 months later. Taxi box always arrived when they said they would and were always helpful. The customer service team were great to deal with too. I wouldn't hesitate to use taxi on again or recommend them to others.
